---
title: Peppercorn Rubbed Steak with Warm Zucchini Antipasti
description: Summer is so close we can taste it! And tonight's meal will have you longing for warm July weather.  Pan-seared steak, juicy zucchini antipasti, and oven-roasted potatoes come together for a weeknight winning meal!
